Changed Processor class. Added textMessage field to store message in the descriptor
Added TextMessage class for the xml tag
Added Processor Interface to process results Added AbstractProcessor class to store main things to process results. Code is partially moved from ProcessorServiceImpl Added ImageProcessor class to process image result Added VideoProcessor class to process video results Changed ProcessorService. Now it takes UserData and VideoData parameters Changed ProcessorServiceImpl class. This takes UserData and VideoData parameters for the method process. Moved logic to process results into other classes. Changed MainController class to pass UserData and VideoData parameters
